{"type":"text","timestamp":1780728921505,"sessionID":"ses_1644b0d2dffeuVNS21qs36MHjG","part":{"id":"prt_e9bb6e85a001dZuYT7uZMv29y8","messageID":"msg_e9bb6dfeb001nPahBSPa0GWUQ5","sessionID":"ses_1644b0d2dffeuVNS21qs36MHjG","type":"text","text":"Recall feedback is a separate implicit signal: searches increment recall counters asynchronously, and the scored search uses recall count as a multiplier. That differs from evolve’s explicit outcome event plus direct weight mutation.","time":{"start":1780728916058,"end":1780728921499},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0b3bb6fd96121daa016a23c4540c8081919de12d407ae7ebdf","phase":"commentary"}}}}
